            "pdf_page_end": 118,
            "bylaw_page_start": 110,
            "bylaw_page_end": 110
          },
          "text": "Every application for a development permit shall be accompanied by plans, in duplicate, drawn to an appropriate scale and showing:"
        },
        {
          "provision_label_raw": "i",
          "clause_path": null,
          "status": "active",
          "citations": {
            "pdf_page_start": 118,
            "pdf_page_end": 118,
            "bylaw_page_start": 110,
            "bylaw_page_end": 110
          },
          "text": "The true shape and dimensions of the lot to be used, and upon which it is proposed to erect any building or structure;"
        },
        {
          "provision_label_raw": "ii",
          "clause_path": null,
          "status": "active",
          "citations": {
            "pdf_page_start": 118,
            "pdf_page_end": 118,
            "bylaw_page_start": 110,
            "bylaw_page_end": 110
          },
          "text": "The proposed location, height and dimensions of the building, structure, or work in respect of which the permit is applied for;"
        },
        {
          "provision_label_raw": "iii",
          "clause_path": null,
          "status": "active",
          "citations": {
            "pdf_page_start": 118,
            "pdf_page_end": 118,
            "bylaw_page_start": 110,
            "bylaw_page_end": 110
          },
          "text": "The location of every building or structure already erected on or partly on such lots, and the location of every building upon contiguous lots;"
        },
        {
          "provision_label_raw": "vi",
          "clause_path": null,
          "status": "active",
          "citations": {
            "pdf_page_start": 118,
            "pdf_page_end": 118,
            "bylaw_page_start": 110,
            "bylaw_page_end": 110
          },
          "text": "The proposed location and dimensions of parking spaces, loading spaces, driveways, and landscaping areas; and"
        },
        {
          "provision_label_raw": "v",
          "clause_path": null,
          "status": "active",
          "citations": {
            "pdf_page_start": 118,
            "pdf_page_end": 118,
            "bylaw_page_start": 110,
            "bylaw_page_end": 110
          },
          "text": "Other such information as may be necessary to determine whether or not every such building, development, re -construction or redevelopment conforms with the requirements of this By-law."
        },
        {
          "provision_label_raw": "b",
          "clause_path": null,
          "status": "active",
          "citations": {
            "pdf_page_start": 118,
            "pdf_page_end": 118,
            "bylaw_page_start": 110,
            "bylaw_page_end": 110
          },
          "text": "Where the Development Officer is unable to determine whether the proposed affect the proposed development, he may require that the plans submitted under this section be based upon an actual survey by a Provincial Land Surveyor."
        }
